    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies. This example exhibits robust mechanical health; the VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has received preventative reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission shifts with precision, channeling power to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable differential lock. The suspension maintains its composure with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the car's celebrated turn-in response and chassis balance. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the performance envelope remains sharp, making this an ideal acquisition for the purist seeking an authentic analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
